1. The big namespace shuffle (make butterfli a little more modular)
  A. Move configuration and specs from butterfli-rails to butterfli

  B. Create butterfli-instagram gem
    - Move in Instagram data model and specs (from butterfli)
    - Move in Instagram configuration model and specs (from butterfli-rails)

  C. Create butterfli-instagram-rails gem
    - Move in Instagram controllers and specs (from butterfli-rails)

  #####
  Butterfli Core

  butterfli (Data framework)
  Butterfli::Story
  Butterfli::Configuration
  Butterfli::Configuration::Providers

  butterfli-dev (Development tools)
  Butterfli::Test::Recorder

  butterfli-rails (API framework for Rails)
  Butterfli::Rails::Engine
  Butterfli::Rails::Controller

  Butterfli Extension

  butterfli-instagram (Instagram data and configuration)
  Butterfli::Instagram (GENERIC) (MODULE)
  Butterfli::Instagram::Data (GENERIC) (DATA) (MODULE)
  Butterfli::Instagram::Data::MediaObject (GENERIC) (DATA) (CLASS)
  Butterfli::Instagram::Configuration::Provider (GENERIC) (API) (CLASS)

  butterfli-instagram-rails
  Butterfli::Instagram::Rails::Engine
  Butterfli::Instagram::Rails::ApiController
  Butterfli::Instagram::Rails::Subscription::GeographyController
